cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning (ML) and its vulnerability to attacks, specifically sybil-based poisoning attacks, in the context of distributed data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the paper discusses attacks and defenses against them. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS) as it deals with distributed data and learning processes. Finally, the paper involves social and information networks (cs.SI) as it discusses the impact of sybils on the distributed learning process.
